them in retrograde form, in inverted form,

79
00:05:22.969 --> 00:05:27.220
and in retrograde-inversion form.

80
00:05:27.220 --> 00:05:30.577
The row starts on E and works to B flat.

81
00:05:32.010 --> 00:05:33.350
The retrograde, of course,

82
