works its way back to the beginning E.

83
00:05:36.850 --> 00:05:40.465
The row starts by moving up a half-step,
and then up a full step.

84
00:05:40.465 --> 00:05:46.430
The inversion starts by going down a half
step and then down a full step, and so on.

85
